title: Cover FX Contour Kit
description:
Take a look at my Cover FX Contour Kit (http://bit.ly/1zoBrzo) review! This is a great cream contour kit with different color options for lots of skin tones!

Also, excuse the cray hair, I wanted to put my hair up so you could see the product better.
